                <h3><a name="freevspaid">Difference between free and paid?</a></h3>

                <p><strong>Free Accounts</strong>
                Free accounts share many of the feature set that paid accounts will have except that they have &#8220;Posted via <a href="blogwith.co">Blogwith</a>&#8221; at the end of their content. </p>

                <p><strong>Paid Accounts</strong>
                 - Will have &#8220;Posted via <a href="blogwith.co">Blogwith</a>&#8221; removed
                 - Ability to manage multiple Wordpress accounts from Evernote
                 - Create Wordpress pages from Evernote
                 - Advanced tags usage. For example:
                 - &#8220;bw_format&#8221;: to set format of the blogpost
                 - &#8220;bw_draft&#8221;: Changes the post&#8217;s status to draft. This post will not be visible to site visitors.
                 - and several others.</p>

                <h3><a name="imagesnotshowing">Images not showing for text posts?</a></h3>

                <p>If you are writing in markdown and you are using the image link. Like this:
                <code>
                ![TITLE](URL_OF_THE_IMAGE)
                </code>
                There is not problem displaying the images. However if you drag and drop images into the note. Blogwith will not process the drag and drop images and your blog post will not show. I&#8217;m current fixing this issue right now and will keep all users posted.</p>

